Titolo: Giga Wrecker

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Giga Wrecker (stylized as GIGA WRECKER) is a puzzle-platform game developed by Game Freak and released for Microsoft Windows in 2017.  Ports to the Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One were released in 2019 as GIGA WRECKER ALT. with additional features.
In Giga Wrecker, the main character Reika smashes obstacles and enemies into debris, then fashions the debris into weapons, balls, cubes, and other tools with which to fight stronger enemies, solve puzzles, and maneuver to new areas.

Genere: Puzzle-platform 

Valutazione: 67
